</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Dav.</SPEAKER>
<P>I have not &s;een him: this it is:&mdash;I told you Marianne had made a former marriage in Flanders; that her hu&s;band after three months left her, went to Paris, and there died. She thought her&s;elf a widow; till this morning after I had left you, and with tran&s;port flew to embrace my bride, I found her bath'd in tears and agoniz'd with grief;&mdash;the impo&s;tor had deceiv'd her; he was living:&mdash;&s;he had &s;een her hu&s;band.</P>
