<P>O &s;hame, &s;hame, &s;hame! and have I liv'd to &s;ee it? O mortal blow to mode&s;ty!&mdash;Let there be no fidelity in woman, no faith henceforth in man!&mdash;Come forth, thou &s;helter'd
