<SP>
<SPEAKER>Dav.</SPEAKER>
<P><STAGE><HI>[To</HI> Dormer.]</STAGE> Dormer, contain your|&s;elf; there's &s;omething here that's dark and ter|rifying: &s;ay nothing to my father;&mdash;let us with|draw, and wait below; there can be no e&s;cape. Nay follow me, I do conjure you.</P>
