</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir H. H.</SPEAKER>
<P>Be caution'd by your Lady, and impute to her concern no other than the pure&s;t motive;&mdash;my life upon it, you will find it &s;uch&punc; Alas, unhappy man, what trea&s;ure have you ca&s;t away? Hear her, con&s;ole her, be advis'd by her: recover, if you can, her forfeited e&s;teem. She is a miracle of goodne&s;s.</P>
