<P>There let me interpo&s;e again. Take a &s;hort time for &s;erious meditation: we will a&s;&s;i&s;t your thoughts. Your friend here has already &s;truck one &s;park of light amid&s;t your dark de&s;pair; patient reflection may bring more in view. Perhaps this meeting with your &s;on, which you in your mind's pre&s;ent agitation are for ha&s;tening, prudence may po&s;tpone.</P>
