</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady D.</SPEAKER>
<P>Oh! if a few calm words can lull your ear, think how repentance may a&s;&s;wage your &s;oul:&mdash;for &s;o much of your offence as falls on me alone, I thank Heaven's mercy for its aid, I can forgive it; nay, my Lord, I have forgiven it.</P>
